                      "marks": [],
                      "value": "In order to deploy the Quarkus application it was necessary to find a provider. To name only a few: Heroku, Azure, Google Cloud, AWS, ... I eventually opted for Oracle Cloud, because they are the only provider with an actual Free Tier and ",
                      "nodeType": "text"
